msgstr "ທຸລະກຳນີ້ບໍ່ໄດ້ຖືກເຊື່ອມໂຍງກັບໂທເຄັນ."

#. module: payment_worldline
#. odoo-python
#: code:addons/payment_worldline/models/payment_transaction.py:0
