msgstr "ການຊຳລະເງິນຂອງທ່ານຖືກຍົກເລີກແລ້ວ."

#. module: payment_worldline
#: model_terms:payment.provider,pending_msg:payment_worldline.payment_provider_worldline
msgid ""
"Your payment has been successfully processed but is waiting for approval."
msgstr "ການຊຳລະເງິນຂອງທ່ານຖືກປະມວນຜົນສຳເລັດແລ້ວ ແຕ່ກຳລັງລໍຖ້າການອະນຸມັດ."

#. module: payment_worldline
#: model_terms:payment.provider,done_msg:payment_worldline.payment_provider_worldline
msgid "Your payment has been successfully processed."
msgstr "ການຊຳລະເງິນຂອງທ່ານໄດ້ຮັບການປະມວນຜົນສຳເລັດແລ້ວ."
